name: MetaFishing [OLD]
description: MetaFishing is a decentralized NFT metaverse game running on BSC, players experience the entertainment brought by the game and earn rewards! In the game, players will play a fishing tycoon in the vast water world. Catch hordes of fish and gain more assets by using rarer NFT.Expand your lands and restore them to the prosperous world of the past!
